d/Chief-of-Army-Staff|title=Chief of Army Staff \u2013 Bangladesh Army|website=www.army.mil.bd|language=en|access-date=2018-07-20}}</ref> (also [[Colonel of the Regiment|Colonel of the Regiment]] \u2013 The East Bengal Regiment; Bangladesh Infantry Regiment; Regiment of Artillery; [[Colonel commandant|Colonel Commandant]] - Armoured Corps; Corps of Engineers ) - 8th [[Bangladesh Military Academy|BMA]] Long Course\n*'''Lieutenant-Generals''' [[File:Three star.jpg|70px]]\n# [[Lieutenant General]] [[Md Mahfuzur Rahman|Md. Mahfuzur Rahman]]  - [[Principal Staff Officer (Bangladesh)|Principal Staff Officer]], [[Armed Forces Division]] ('''PSO AFD'''), [[Prime Minister's Office (Bangladesh)|Prime Minister's Office]] <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.afd.gov.bd/media-center/important-occations/22-sidebar/45-lieutenant-general-md-mahfuzur-rahman-rcds-ndc-afwc-psc-phd.html|title=Lieutenant General Md Mahfuzur Rahman,rcds, ndc,  afwc, psc, PhD|last=Division|first=Armed Forces|website=www.afd.gov.bd|language=en-gb|access-date=2018-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180720195120/https://www.afd.gov.bd/media-center/important-occations/22-sidebar/45-lieutenant-general-md-mahfuzur-rahman-rcds-ndc-afwc-psc-phd.html|archive-date=2018-07-20|url-status=dead}}</ref> - 5th BMA Long Course\n# Lieutenant General [[Shafiqur Rahman (officer)|Shafiqur Rahman]] \u2013 [[Chief of the General Staff|Chief of the General Staff]] ('''CGS'''), Army Headquarters, Dhaka Cantonment <ref name=\"Shafiqur\">{{cite web|url=http://www.theindependentbd.com/printversion/details/160187|title=Shafiqur made CGS, Mujibur new DG of SSF|website=theindependentbd.com|date=July 31, 2018|accessdate=August 2, 2018}}</ref> - 11th BMA Long Course\n# Lieutenant General [[Shamsul Haque]] \u2013 [[Quartermaster general|Quartermaster-General]] ('''QMG'''), Army Headquarters, Dhaka Cantonment - 10th BMA Long Course\n# Lieutenant General [[Shafiuddin Ahmed (officer)|Shafiuddin Ahmed]]  \u2013 [[General officer comma