y Observer|access-date=2018-03-08|language=en}}</ref> - 16th BMA Long Course\n# Major General  [[Mohammad Humayun Kabir|Humayun Kabir]] \u2013 ('''GOC''') 55th Infantry Division & Area Commander, [[Jashore]] Area, [[Jashore District]] - 13th BMA Long Course\n# Major General Nazrul Islam \u2013 ('''GOC''') 66th Infantry Division & Area Commander, [[Rangpur, Bangladesh|Rangpur]] Area, [[Rangpur District]] - 17th  BMA Long course\n# Major General Akbar Hossain \u2013 Commandant, [[Defence Services Command and Staff College (Bangladesh)|Defence Services Command and Staff College]] ('''Commandant DSCSC'''), Mirpur Cantonment <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dscsc.mil.bd/HbCommandant|title=Honour Board Commandant  \u2013 DSCSC|last=Habib|first=Asif Kibria, Mishel Tanvir|website=www.dscsc.mil.bd|access-date=2018-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180301164907/https://www.dscsc.mil.bd/HbCommandant|archive-date=2018-03-01|url-status=dead}}</ref> - 13th BMA Long Course\n# Major General [[Anwarul Momen]] \u2013 Commandant, [[Bangladesh Military Academy]] ('''Commandant BMA'''), [[Bhatiari|Bhatiary]], Chittagong - 12th BMA Long Course\n#'''Vacant''' \u2013 Commandant, [[Bangladesh Institute of Peace Support Operations Training]] ('''Commandant BIPSOT'''), [[Rajendrapur Cantonment]] <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bipsot.net/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=54&Itemid=194|title=Present Setup \u2013 BIPSOT|last=Administrator|first=Net|website=www.bipsot.net|language=en-gb|access-date=2018-03-01}}</ref> \n# Major General Wahid-uz-Zaman- Commandant, [[Military Institute of Science and Technology|Military Institute of Science and Technology]] ('''Commandant MIST'''), Mirpur Cantonment, Dhaka - 17th BMA Long Course\n#Major General Shahinul Haque \u2013 Commandant, [[School of Infantry and Tactics|School of Infantry and Tactics]] ('''Commandant SI&T'''), [[Jalalabad Cantonment]], [[Sylhet Division|Sylhet]] - 20th BMA Long Course\n# Major General Ataul Hakim Sarwar Hasan  \u2013 [[Chancellor (education)|Vice Chancellor]], [[Bangladesh University of Professionals]] ('''VC BUP'''), Mirpur Cantonment, Dhaka - 11th BMA Long Course\n#'''Vacant''' - College Secretary, [[National Defence College (Bangladesh)|National Defence College]] (NDC), Mirpur Cantonment, Dhaka\n#Major General Jahirul Islam \u2013 Senior Directing Staff (Army-1),  [[National Defence College (Bangladesh)|National Defence College]] (NDC), [[Mirpur Cantonment]] - 19th BMA Long Course\n# [[Major General]] Asheek-uz-Zaman - Senior Directing Staff (Army-2) , [[National Defence College (Bangladesh)|National Defence College]] (NDC), Mirpur Cantonment - 18th BMA Long Course<ref>https://www.ndc.gov.bd/Page/FacultyStaff/NDC_Faculty/1</ref>\n# '''Vacant''' - Senior Directing Staff (Army-3), [[National Defence College (Bangladesh)|National Defence College]] (NDC), Mirpur Cantonment<ref>https://www.ndc.gov.bd/Page/FacultyStaff/NDC_Faculty/1</ref>\n# [[Major General]] Dr. Md Fashiur Rahman '''AMC''' \u2013 Director General, Directorate General Medical Service '''(DG DGMS)''', Dhaka Cantonment (also Colonel Commandant \u2013 Army Medical Corps)\n# [[Major General]] Dr. Md Azizul Islam '''AMC'''\u2013 Consultant Physician General, Directorate General of Medical Services (CPG DGMS), Dhaka Cantonment\n# [[Major General]] Dr. Mahbubur Rahman '''AMC''' \u2013 Consultant Surgeon General, Directorate General Of Medical Services (CSG DGMS), Dhaka Cantonment\n# [[Major General]] Dr. Golam Mohiuddin Chowdhory '''ADC''' \u2013 Dental Surgeon General, Directorate General of Medical Services (DSG DGMS), Dhaka Cantonment (also Colonel Commandant \u2013 Army Dental Corps)\n# [[Major General]] Dr. Mustafizur Rahman '''AMC''' \u2013 Commandant, [[Armed Forces Medical College (Bangladesh)|Armed Forces Medical College]] (AFMC), Dhaka Cantonment\n# [[Major General]] Dr. Mahbubur Rahman '''AMC''' \u2013 Director General, Directorate General Drug Administration (DG DGDA), Dhaka <ref>{{Cite web|ur